CENTROWANIE TEXTU W RAMCE

<div class="ramka">
 <span>Długi lub krótki text blablalblalskjhkshdg;skhdjg; </span>
</div>
CSS:
.ramka{
	text-align: center;
	border: 5px solid #bdc9ca;
	padding: 10px;
	width: 100%;
	min-height: 200px;
	line-height: 200px;<!-- this one must be set
}
.ramka > span
{
	display: inline-block;
	vertical-align: middle;
	line-height: 22px; /* <-- adjust this */
}
=============================================================================================
obcinanie obrazków w CSS
<div class="image-holder">
 <img class="image-class">
</div>
------------ css
.image-holder{
 position: relative;
}
.image-class{
  position: absolute;
  max-width:370px;//max-width: dowolny
  clip: rect(0px 370px 240px 0px);
}
